{"tid":1466900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《警世》咪撚再捉戰犯啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:28:11.000Z","uid":137459,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d300dfd5e6a4d2fca51cef4edc89348770c4a988","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:23.000Z","msg":"擺到明對家一直有mon住連登，再睇住我地黎食啦。<br />\n六月到依家，我地覺得邊到適合作戰嘅地點佢偏唔批不反對通知書。<br />\n727元朗遊行我地focus係小心鄉黑佢就偏唔出。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目的就係想我地互屌、分化、割蓆。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n老實講，好多時即使我地嘅行動有缺陷，甚至達成唔到共識，<span style=\"color: red;\">但只要我地仲有團火，都唔會導致我地爭取民主自由運動失敗。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真正會導致運動失敗往往都係比人分化，之後互屌，最後大家冇癮散水。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好多手足都已經提過，見到三毛嘅捉戰犯/指罵post，記得直接負評上一頁。<br />\n<br />\n遇到突發事、或者想檢討行動不足，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請focus係行動post亡羊補牢。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後請大家記得，對<span style=\"color: red;\">同路人嘅標準同語氣不能苛刻</span>，畢竟大家背景、性格、經歷都不一樣，要達成絕對共識係冇可能。只要不偏離大方向，包容係必要。"},{"pid":"75c933fc7408bc027fb0c3f550d07950f8b37d14","tid":1466900,"uid":95487,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524665fe713c48c6e970e3994f34686a7cce89e5","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa8403bfe660e72ff3b9847d30b036c095d6910c","tid":1466900,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>獨立思考！<br />\n<br />\n點解咁容易帶到風向？因為<span style=\"color: red;\">好多人根本冇獨立思考</span>，邊度吹風就跟邊度走<br />\n<br />\n同時亦要善用科技，多方求證消息</strong><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"9c34474d8608a17d925ae9a8bde72736478d8e5f","tid":1466900,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:11.000Z","msg":"[捉鬼大師]鬼 從來係無需要捉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460872\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460872</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4d61886f8408c425c1c6f793a783f808ee55afda","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895a68fb4e70dd16a5eb0d7d17ffc531405ddbb1","tid":1466900,"uid":46340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 「唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。」<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰！！！<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b16bcd826c435ce745aab4011d5092ca5b46061","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf6d34b0aeab8fd2d5154b6c69e1e2c33e5a68f","tid":1466900,"uid":188432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:49.000Z","msg":"(集思廣益長文) 求大家用2分鐘時間睇睇 解決問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"486e22c3cf520c504722638bbbca752bb03948c0","tid":1466900,"uid":77533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:19.000Z","msg":"推，過左點半唔想再見到互屌同捉鬼post"},{"pid":"564d436b419596e7ce6ee7febe17b71a08788cb3","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a8a652a9200f0fc9b796e6e71742a2efa7230f","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3adb04e95831f6c8edbbd964cb953c989608da6","tid":1466900,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>聽日一定要做！！！！<br />\n<br />\n理撚得佢有冇鬼！！！！<br />\n<br />\n讓條路俾旅客，然後禮貌鞠躬道歉！！！！<br />\n<br />\n今晚大家早d翻去，準備文宣！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c6423a8a51c6f1760a787fb4f81ab7e2eebcc084","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79ed10d2db58777951a3399ff58f6b401274c612","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfcce4c8e74d8b90bb2296c60a78da3f86dae783","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7adb1dbf4fb89250bedd6693afbf21f70b9a845e","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00a57e246f1c5b045b2e6bb81e12c92217df30d","tid":1466900,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:43.000Z","msg":"大家捉鬼分化搞咁耐，係時候做返正經事推正經Post<br />\n<br />\n&rsquo;呢兩日機場𣎴合作運動雖然成功搞到經濟，但無可否認係有失民意，縱觀兩日運動情況<br />\n尋日係人多，但大叫廣東話令遊客好難明白發生咩事<br />\n今日就唔洗講，唔夠人唯有塞路<br />\n<br />\n但事實上國際支持都好重要，機場除咗經濟問題，暫時其實仲有另一個天大優勢<br />\n<br />\n目前為止唯一一個可以比示威者唔受傷地表達訴求嘅地方！<br />\n<br />\n我地要做嘅係打M男同情牌，我地唔想阻到你，但香港人已經流了太多血，唔想再受傷！<br />\n<br />\nPOPO每日做嘅野過分十萬倍千萬倍點解仲有咁多藍絲廢老中立派支持？<br />\n因為佢地會做門面野，會開記招發布對自己有利既訊息，你可能笑on9<br />\n但肯定有唔少藍絲會信覺得你班廢青搞事<br />\n<br />\n機場同時係一個好機會，比和理非做盾去Cover勇武巴打<br />\n大量文宣鋪天蓋地，除非外國人自私到仆街，唔係點都會可憐下你<br />\n<br />\n我夠膽講，係示弱方面，香港人認第二，無人夠膽認第一<br />\n<br />\n呢啲時候M文宣就好重要，去到今日都未到對國際用文宣真係要檢討，首先我地要<br />\n<br />\n1.清晰五大訴求嘅slogan，等遊客知我地發生咩事<br />\n2.打多啲同情牌，必要時之前跪住叫人擺工嘅方法可以再用，表面功夫要做足，我地係比香港政府逼到絕路先阻到你<br />\n3.人多！！！講幾多嘢都無用，無人實收皮<br />\n<br />\n最簡單可以喺機場話I am sorry for any inconvenience. Please contact your country's embassy for protection NOW. It helps you as well as exerting pressure on HKGOV.<br />\n咁樣明面上打同情牌，暗地鍊住政府春袋，就可以出師有名！最重要係畫面！你想NOW或者外國媒體報導將Cover係你搞喊小朋友定跪係度求遊客原諒？三罷個陣連廢老都跪，而家點解和理非唔可以Cover勇武合理化成件事？就算黑警清場，輿論上都唔會係驅趕一班搞旅客既人！<br />\n<br />\n用埋同理心，機場人多無wifi，好多旅客除咗白等係唔知應該點做的，想上網search點做都唔得。<br />\n呢個時候最需係指引遊客可以點做，例如租酒店，claim保險，附近邊度有酒店，搵航班同AA投訴或者claim錢，總之將個問題射落比政府機構，避免示威者同遊客對立<br />\n<br />\n點樣達至最大效益？當然係將呢啲資訊同文宣夾埋一齊整成小册子，大家都想要呢本嘢，令香港情況更易輸出比國際，亦都做返示威者友善一面比國際睇，拎返民意<br />\n<br />\n我會建議小冊子有以下內容<br />\n1.點解要反送中<br />\n2.五大訴求<br />\n3.示威者被逼壓，被傷害嘅圖，每頁有埋Qr code可以睇埋相關濫權合集<br />\n4.道歉！阻到你唔好意思，但呢度係唯一唔洗比狗射嘅地方<br />\n5.有資料點求助，將個波推比政府<br />\n<br />\n咁文宣黎講要超級M，將和理非嘅作用放到最大，亦都係和理非可以cover勇武手足嘅機會！<br />\n<br />\n認同入post做文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464891</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0c2264f67f7565b164c20f26529ff3ad7739b48e","tid":1466900,"uid":3416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"daf36639c0f2e93a4d4d3a24af8ab458b95ce32b","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8b981069d7a7ea74625e955d1c081e6adcd5a2e","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cab485ab0fec2e9adc5663fb310985cee9e5fabf","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c0d92daceffcc8cc2a7427e9bb871c0f098077c","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"293e1b2c37c864c23f4ce24d1881bf99ac5fa03c","tid":1466900,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47351ef9009a01004481d146514fc0f68a8dbf8","tid":1466900,"uid":16256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:44.000Z","msg":"推814 1點"}]}